longBusinessSummary: Medhelp Care Aktiebolag (publ), a software-as-a-service company, operates a health platform for data-driven corporate health and supports in Sweden and Denmark. The company offers absence management, sickness absence statistics, health care advice, and rehabilitation support. Medhelp Care Aktiebolag (publ) was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
